# Ignore Liquid Variables
\{\{\s*.*\s*\}\}
\{\%\s*.*\s*\%\}
\{\{\s*post\.link\s*\}\}
\{\{\s*base_path\s*\}\}
\{\{\s*site\.baseurl\s*\}\}

# Ignore Template Folders
_includes/
_layouts/
_sass/

# Ignore common placeholders
https://www.linkedin.com/in/\{\{.*\}\}
https://twitter.com/\{\{.*\}\}
https://github.com/\{\{.*\}\}
https://www.facebook.com/\{\{.*\}\}
https://www.instagram.com/\{\{.*\}\}

# Ignore specific broken legacy links identified in logs
https://api.staticman.net/v1/entry/.*
